News.Title: Influx Healthtech Expands Production Capacity with New High-Speed Capsule Machine
News.Summary: Influx Healthtech has acquired a new high-speed capsule machine that will increase production capacity from 23,000 to 145,000 capsules per hour. The expansion has been fully funded internally and the machine is expected to be operational this month.

News.Title: Influx HealthTech to Launch New Manufacturing Facility in Thane
News.Summary: Influx HealthTech is set to commence operations at a new manufacturing facility located in Thane. The company aims to expand its production capabilities by increasing the number of tablet granulation lines in the near future. This move suggests a strategic expansion of Influx HealthTech's manufacturing capacity in the pharmaceutical sector.
